the movie is amazing so go see it. if u havnt seen the first one, or if u havnt seen it in a really long time i recommend u do cuz if not ull be lost. this is the best pirate movie ive seen with awesome twists, some PG sexy scenes lol, and witty humor. "There will come a moment when ull have the chance to do the right thing." -Elizabeth
"i love those moments...I like to wave at them as they pass by"-jack sparrow
